posting_body: ['The Presidio Landmark', '1801 Wedemeyer St, San Francisco, CA, 94129-5274', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 5', 'OR Text', '5', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'BEAUTY AND SUSTAINABILITY', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 1000 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The Presidio Landmark offers residents a unique combination of history, natural beauty and breathtaking views - all with majestic views of the city, ocean and breathtaking national park.', 'This national landmark has been sustainability renovated, appointed with modern amenities, interiors, thoughtful services including a 24/7 concierge.', 'To top it all off, it’s all just five minutes to Crissy Field and the Golden Gate Bridge.', 'Pet Policy', 'Located in a Federal Park, there are no pets allowed.', "For Service/Emotional Support animals, doctor's note and a Special Accommodations form will be needed.", 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'IPJE74GfLRq']
